Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.34,0:00:19.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Woke up with yawning,\Nit's dawning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.96,0:00:22.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still alive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:27.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Turned on my radio\NTo start up new day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.87,0:00:30.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As goddamned D.J. chattered
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.78,0:00:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How to survive
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:39.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing news got over\NOn that air wave
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:45.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:49.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:50.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:55.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.28,0:01:01.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-night, good-night
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:06.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She's a shooting star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:10.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good-bye…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:16.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NLove is rationed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.42,0:01:19.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight,\NAcross the nation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight\NLove reflects world wide
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Almost another day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.96,0:01:28.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,See you some other day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.72,0:01:45.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long Kurosaki\Nand Renji are going to train.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.94,0:01:47.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.40,0:01:50.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we should let them run amuck\Nuntil they're satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:54.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. That fool is depressed\Njust because he lost once…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.25,0:01:57.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah…you're right…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.25,0:02:02.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?!\NWill fighting make him feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.68,0:02:05.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Idiots sure are simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:10.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, what happened\Nbetween Ishida and Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:14.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida was really worried\Nabout Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.44,0:02:18.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?\NThe Bounts are our enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.57,0:02:20.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What good would it do to worry\Nabout an enemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah… Anyway, we’ve a lot of\Nquestions to ask that woman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,once she recovers a bit more…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:31.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm exhausted…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:36.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We got carried away and\Nnow it's morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:41.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, breakfast has been prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.77,0:02:45.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I even prepared some\Nfor the freeloader!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:47.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That always bothers me…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:49.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.74,0:02:51.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The store owner is in the back
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,repairing Lirin and the others’ gigai.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.31,0:02:55.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Want some coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:56.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:02:59.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:05.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.51,0:03:08.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's gross!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this disgusting drink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's coffee…\NDon't you know what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.00,0:03:20.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.60,0:03:23.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Renji, can't you drink coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.89,0:03:26.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want some sugar in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.76,0:03:31.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sugar?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:33.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You put in sugar to drink it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:34.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange tea…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.25,0:03:46.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little more…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.68,0:03:49.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One more…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:51.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How much of a sweet tooth\Ndo you have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:55.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?\NIt sure is noisy this morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.48,0:03:56.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:03:58.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:05.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you've gotten over it…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was quite a pain…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This guy was completely depressed…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I wasn't that depressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:17.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.08,0:04:18.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that look?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:21.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fine…\NLet's start from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:22.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:24.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow… That looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:27.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You have a good eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.18,0:04:29.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I used french toast as a base and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:32.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,spread melted bean jam on it\Nin place of honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.22,0:04:34.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's bean jam toast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.01,0:04:35.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're still making things like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.93,0:04:40.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia, do you know
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–how to drink this coffee thing?\N–It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:47.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NI've already cleared that drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.63,0:04:49.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh. That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.07,0:04:50.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.92,0:04:56.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A brief rest between battles…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:05:01.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A happy circle of friends.\NWhat a great thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:05.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Noba?\NAre you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.80,0:05:08.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bount…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:11.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoshino's presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:16.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes. It seems she left\Nthe premises a bit earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.17,0:05:21.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but we're all adults who can take\Nresponsibility for our own actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:25.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something we should\Nbe making a fuss about each time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, disturbing this\Nhappy morning circle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with troubling information is stressful…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can tell them later\Nwhen things have calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:35.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:46.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Master Kariya, I had everyone besides us\Nhead to that location, as you commanded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.32,0:05:48.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:12.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fixing a broken clock will once again\Nstart the motion of time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:16.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,For Bounts, time was stopped\Nfrom the very beginning…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:21.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Even if our gears are fixed,\Nand wound up, it will never move…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.12,0:06:28.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Humans live with time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.63,0:06:34.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They reject us Bounts…\NWe just exist. That's it…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:41.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Bounts have time that doesn't flow,\Nand are despised by humans…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.94,0:06:47.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But… We will try to move\Nthat motionless time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:50.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will change fate ourselves…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:52.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in order to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.83,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,URAHARA'S SHOP
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.59,0:07:15.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.95,0:07:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are your wounds okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:21.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You had pretty serious injuries,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.75,0:07:24.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's none of my concern…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:25.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a second!\NWhat are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.65,0:07:33.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch a lady so familiarly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.55,0:07:35.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where are we going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:37.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you track Yoshino's\NSpiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:41.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino? Is Yoshino\Nthat old Bount lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.52,0:07:45.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nher presence wasn't in the house…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.46,0:07:47.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me where Yoshino is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.30,0:07:52.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:56.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\None disappeared this morning…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:57.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:07:59.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Another one?\NNo. Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.88,0:08:05.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What disappeared?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm…well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.58,0:08:09.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Their presence disappeared…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.28,0:08:11.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–Presence?\N–Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! A presence.\NPre-sence!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.06,0:08:17.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's this fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:20.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\NLirin sure is late…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she's still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.28,0:08:27.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–As I was saying…\N–What is it? I want to join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.25,0:08:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You've come…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.05,0:09:01.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really plan to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well…who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.25,0:09:09.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put an end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.55,0:09:11.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.91,0:09:14.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Which way?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.08,0:09:17.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm getting dizzy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't swing me around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:20.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This way?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.08,0:09:22.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it this way? Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:29.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! I'm getting dizzy and\Ngetting even more confused!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.92,0:09:33.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You said that it still wasn't time yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The situation has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world changed?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you curious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.60,0:09:47.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:54.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I need your help…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:55.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.63,0:09:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeig dih, Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:14.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want, Yoshino?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're my alter ego, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:19.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.24,0:10:23.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any problems\Nwith dying here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:25.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to die together?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.75,0:10:27.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Back here again?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:36.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.52,0:10:38.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that Bounts are fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.25,0:10:49.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.71,0:10:57.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.59,0:11:00.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe, calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.13,0:11:04.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.24,0:11:05.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you go, you'll just be in the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.08,0:11:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.87,0:11:25.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Yoshino,\NIshida, and Lirin, have left…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.05,0:11:26.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us that sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried many times!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:33.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Now's not the time\Nto be quarreling!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.70,0:11:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.14,0:11:37.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, let's go after Ishida\Nand the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:41.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Noba, do you know\Nwhere they're heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:42.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.22,0:11:45.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.05,0:11:46.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.71,0:11:52.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–Don’t tell me you're trying to stop…\N–No… But this is a race against time…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.88,0:11:56.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki and Abarai,\Nrun ahead of us with Flash Step.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We will catch up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:12:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–All right!\N–Also…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:07.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to get Ishida back,\Nwe should avoid a fight if possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:34.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all right…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:38.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe, fight as you please\Nwithout concern for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:40.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you rushing to your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:42.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jin…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.32,0:12:45.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.18,0:12:48.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's amazing that you can use\Na doll in your condition…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:58.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We control this world's great power\Nwith these crests.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.22,0:13:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But if our balance is lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,our power goes out of control\Nand attacks us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.85,0:13:11.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that\Nyou can summon a doll
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.13,0:13:14.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or even freely control one\Nin your decrepit state…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:19.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what happens to me\Nif I can stop you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:25.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's wrong…\NYou really don't know your own worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:26.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:32.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your doll, Goethe, doesn't have\Nsubservient feelings towards you…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.01,0:13:34.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has feelings of love…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.55,0:13:38.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That is because even though\Nwe cannot leave descendants,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.92,0:13:44.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you're the only Bount\Nwho has a maternal power…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:46.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:52.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quincy boy, I know you're here…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.19,0:13:55.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How about coming out?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.65,0:13:59.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You! Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't just let\Na pitiful woman die alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:08.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:15.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with me…\Na Quincy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:19.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A Quincy without his powers…\Nis useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:21.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have a use for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:25.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But since you’re here…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.16,0:14:27.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you something interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,–What do you plan to do?!\N–Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino… I can't move…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:41.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.40,0:14:45.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:46.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:49.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is as far as you'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:51.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You won't pass here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An important ritual is about to begin…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:14:58.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ritual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let things go\Nthe way you want them to!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.49,0:15:03.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Zabimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.05,0:15:05.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guard, Dalk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.32,0:15:11.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fine… This is boring,\Nbut I'll play with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is this ritual!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.94,0:15:21.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.74,0:15:24.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do with her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.71,0:15:28.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino has a maternal power…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Maternal?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.30,0:15:33.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From past experience,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:36.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that my targeted power\Ncannot be achieved
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,by just sucking the souls\Nof living humans…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:45.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And when I researched\Nthe best way to absorb souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.69,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I arrived at this woman's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.89,0:15:54.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be glad! You're going to become a mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.88,0:15:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NYou'll breathe life into new dolls!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.97,0:16:02.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.98,0:16:08.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.44,0:16:22.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.43,0:16:30.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You still want to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.30,0:16:40.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How admirable…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:44.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.77,0:16:55.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take your eyes off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.32,0:17:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The crest is…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Etched in his body…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.46,0:17:15.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jin has…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.94,0:17:19.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fused his own body with his doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.00,0:17:21.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's right…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.49,0:17:27.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes… You were always strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.36,0:17:30.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And will continue to be strong…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:34.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was only used…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:36.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a foolish woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:38.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:39.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:47.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you plan to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.59,0:17:50.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.80,0:17:53.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:22.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Goethe…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshi…no…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.88,0:18:29.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're together until the end…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:33.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mama…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.79,0:18:37.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you fused with your doll,\Nas I thought you would…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go…Goethe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:19.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,She lost her crest.\NBut she's not absorbed by the doll…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:22.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Yoshino's\Nmaternal spiritual power…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.60,0:19:27.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.58,0:19:29.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're floating in mid-air?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.25,0:19:33.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! What in the world\Nis going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.58,0:19:35.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This power is what I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.04,0:19:51.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…it would be bad if\NI let it wither away here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.25,0:20:00.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.38,0:20:12.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:15.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.10,0:20:21.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.71,0:20:25.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!\NTh-That’s…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.63,0:20:33.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine.\NThis way of dying is fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.59,0:20:35.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.88,0:20:38.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What direct eyes…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.56,0:20:44.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, proud, last Quincy…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:07.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was waiting for this moment…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Zeigt euch, neue leben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:24.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshino…\Nyour life shall be newly reborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.92,0:21:28.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:31.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.31,0:21:33.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.96,0:21:35.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:51.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's as we planned!\NThe birth of a new doll!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.61,0:21:55.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! More!\NMore must be born!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:10.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.49,0:22:11.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:31.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:36.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The flowers glow and fade away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.30,0:22:51.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sky falls silent,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.11,0:22:57.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as a pair of\Ndreamy fireworks (Hanabi) lit up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.28,0:23:04.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will sing my piercing love to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:15.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blooming in an instant\Nare fireworks (Hanabi)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.62,0:23:22.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sky blue dreams shine and flicker,\Ndancing away into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.37,0:23:26.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Blossom away in full bloom, high above
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:31.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Protect and keep those feelings thriving
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.50,0:23:37.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Strongly, at least till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.35,0:23:45.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,These flowers will glow and fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.27,0:23:59.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What were those bird-like things?\NOne of Lirin's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.10,0:24:02.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How insulting!\NI'm the blue bird of luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:05.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you think of yourself as?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.00,0:24:07.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you more like a cursed doll?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.26,0:24:10.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?! How insulting!\NI'll put a curse on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:21.82,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:24.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.81,0:24:27.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kyoraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.40,0:24:28.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.32,0:24:32.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Old Gramps Yama took\Nhis time to summon me…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.05,0:24:35.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be anything ordinary…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.03,0:24:38.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Old gramps Yama…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.21,0:24:40.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.80,0:24:41.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.26,0:24:44.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Nanao…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.24,0:24:44.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.29,0:24:49.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That old man called me,\Nbut he’s sleeping…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.51,0:24:51.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he is old…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.79,0:24:59.79,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tune in again!